{"tid":2284290,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好無記性？！","createTime":"2020-11-13T07:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T09:44:01.000Z","uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85f4f5702ff57aefe6fd9092a678d08ea8f25d0f","tid":2284290,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"我係車台開咗幾個考車唔合格嘅post <br />\n<br />\n有好多巴打絲打入黎留言話自己都fail或者pass笑我廢咁<br />\n<br />\n我好想同佢地做互動 記低佢地個名<br />\n<br />\n但我完全記唔到 轉個頭就唔記得邊個打邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只記得輸民意巴打 jer仔巴打同被訓斥絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他個啲大部分都唔記得<br />\n<br />\n我係咪有病？要唔要睇醫生？做過三次全身麻醉手術 唔知有無影響？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0ad214e4dc09890fc25caa4ec2a0b5549c0249","tid":2284290,"uid":257705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T07:53:47.000Z","msg":"？"},{"pid":"d959a826ae7542299fcbfd289711766eaff251a3","tid":2284290,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed0ad214e4dc09890fc25caa4ec2a0b5549c0249","tid":2284290,"uid":257705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T07:53:47.000Z","msg":"？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"我都記得你 hater黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a0e76217da40cdf09e00fcf41a1a65dacde664","tid":2284290,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T08:10:01.000Z","msg":"返工又係 老闆提咗我好多次 但我都記唔到 好彩佢好好人 咁先無俾人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n特別係啲步驟 過一星期就唔記得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm